{"tid":368961,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"［會計］為同行RSM核數失職 英Pwc再被重罰千","createTime":"2017-08-22T02:47:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-22T03:30:14.000Z","uid":40770,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e35151a98acc9d8cf2247dae0888cd7c923c171a","tid":368961,"uid":40770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T02:47:49.000Z","msg":"會計「四大」PwC行為不當 再遭天價重罰510萬英鎊<br />\n<br />\n2017/08/17 11:10<br />\n(圖片來源：AFP)<br />\n(圖片來源：AFP)<br />\n英國會計監管單位 Financial Reporting Council (FRC) 周三 (16 日) 宣布，對在英國 PwC 課以高達 510 萬英鎊 (660 萬美元) 的罰金，因後者替財務管理顧問公司 RSM Tenon 所做的審計工作行為不當。這也創下該機構有史以來祭出的最高罰金紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n事涉 PwC 於 2011 年 6 月結束的會計年度，為 RSM Tenon 所提供的審計服務，PwC 一高級合夥人 Nicholas Boden 如今也遭 FRC 處罰。PwC 在聲明中表示，他們對於 2011 年的審計工作有部分未達專業標準感到遺憾，並持續審查及更新公司的審計程序，以回應內部審查與外部監督所發現的情事。<br />\n<br />\nPwC 今年 5 月才因替 Connaught Plc 所做的審計行為不當，遭 FRC 處以 500 萬英鎊 (640 萬美元) 罰金，當時已是該機構的最高罰金紀錄。FRC 今日補充，原本對 PwC 課處的罰金是 600 萬英鎊，但因和解而降低罰金。不過，PwC 還必須支付 50 萬英鎊的費用予 FRC。<br />\n<br />\nRSM Tenon 及 Connaught 已分別於 2013 年及 2010 年宣告破產。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.telegraph.co.uk/business/2017/08/16/pwc-hit-largest-ever-fine-financial-watchdog-rsm-tenon-audit/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraph.co.uk%2Fbusiness%2F2017%2F08%2F16%2Fpwc-hit-largest-ever-fine-financial-watchdog-rsm-tenon-audit%2F&d=oyRL%2FsHzh4EwljRoU5dkLL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=680e133d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.telegraph.co.uk/business/2017/08/16/pwc-hit-largest-ever-fine-financial-watchdog-rsm-tenon-audit/</a>"},{"pid":"d041da3e606bf21648708272a4e0f79caef39eee","tid":368961,"uid":72280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T03:16:10.000Z","msg":"點解 big4好似個個月都被人罰"},{"pid":"151fba81de34715fc52143b838dae8911a9e8bf0","tid":368961,"uid":39012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T03:18:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解 big4好似個個月都被人罰</blockquote><br />\n收人錢財替人消災"},{"pid":"7043e3151ed84c299c9cf009c434f60